{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 260.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was thoroughly worsted in the concentration camp life and in the nature of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he left absolutely nothing to the imagination.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can I recall my thoughts?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you think somebody thinks when he's told that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look up at the smoke, and see there goes your mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have no thoughts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are devastated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you are-- you are drained of all normal mental processes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Your mind doesn't function.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the mind is accustomed to function.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- your mind becomes a black hole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You-- you can't disbelieve, and you can't believe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can't fail to accept, but you can't realize it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Again, it was also part of the whole process of dehumanization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Perhaps this not planned by the Germans, because this was, as I say, a very unusual and fortuitous event.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the fact that people could, even if only as a rumor, hear, or even if they did not believe the odor or the sight of the smoke, even if it was only a doubt that was gnawing away at your mind, it completely devastated your mental processes.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You were not an ordinary human being on the planet Earth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You were mentally, certainly, a zombie on a different planet, maybe a little green man on Mars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kept me going, me, you know, and people like myself, in the literature on the Holocaust, they say-- they are very clear on this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who are aware and politically conscious, had a better chance of mental survival than those who were not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Intellectuals and intelligentsia may have had a diminished physical capacity or facility for survival than people, for instance, who were accustomed to heavy labor all through their life, or who were physically in better condition than the average intellectual would be.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
